channel.title: Forum images aren't loading.
channel.description:
I do apologize if this has been touched on but I'm not really able to navigate the site much with no forum images showing up at all. I don't think it's my computer since this is the third computer I have checked on. Is the site undergoing maintenance or having issues contacting certain files? The only thing in place of the images are blue squares with question marks in them. Just want to figure out what the issue is, thanks. :slight_smile:
EDIT: Dear God, only after I post do I see the "Forums issues" sticky. Sorry guys. :facepalm:
EDIT2: While this is still here, to give more insight on my situation. I tried both IE, MF, and Safari, and both Mac and Windows OS'. Same results and load times are about 10 seconds a page. My net is responding properly for other sites however. WHAT DID YOU DO HUBI!
